{"tid":1524324,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日全世界同我入機場、坐黨鐵唔好撚比錢，跳閘入去算","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:32:33.000Z","uid":180201,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"473b1d18b1058d1377c626d3252e864d467c0b79","tid":1524324,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母<br />\n黨鐵停撚晒5條線？<br />\n比班黑警咁撚樣打人同嚇人？<br />\n你真係覺得我地會好撚驚？<br />\n你咁做只會令我地更加嬲呀屌你老母臭閪！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你班傻鳩黑警比啲政治人物利用緊都唔撚知？</span><br />\n依家全世界、你啊頭都想你死啊！<br />\n你地真係好撚忠誠，忠誠個啲狗。<br />\n啲狗都起碼會咬下主人啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲<br />\n好撚嬲<br />\n好撚嬲<br />\n全世界入機場<br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲，幫推+文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚嬲，但唔想出嚟，怕落雨又乜柒，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5857a308dd5bf23b57c716dd9440e056059df2aa","tid":1524324,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:02.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n開始"},{"pid":"eda060ed4baf75ffc80496b7242f943aec5c4c78","tid":1524324,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/xbt92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fxbt92&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70v%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=e5b67915\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/xbt92</a><br />\nPOPO唔俾救護落站，市民要用M山止血<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h70jL37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh70jL37.jpg&h=2a507755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdSNUXw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfdSNUXw.jpg&h=10124c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#HongKongProtest<br />\n#hkpolicebrutality<br />\n#antielab<br />\n#terroristhkpolice<br />\n#terroristhkpolice<br />\n#whatishappeninginhk<br />\n#whatishappeninginhongkong<br />\n#what